            "title": "明登場兩新股暗盤中段齊造好 群核科技暫較招股價高逾1.5倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">明天再有兩隻新股掛牌，其中包括「杭州六小龍」之一的群核科技(00068)，該股今日暗盤表現亦甚佳，於暗盤中段已較招股價高逾1.5倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：群核科技官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Manycore-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：群核科技官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260330_FI_source-web_Manycore-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：群核科技官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至下午約5時14分，輝立交易平台顯示群核科技暗盤報19.3元，較招股價高1.53倍；富途顯示的暗盤價為20.1元，較招股價高1.64倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">同樣在明天登場的長光辰芯(03277)，暗盤表現也絕不失禮。輝立交易平台顯示暗盤暫報68.65元，高於招股價逾72%；富途交易平台的暗盤暫報68.75元，亦高於招股價72.39%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15881552-%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e4%b8%ad%e6%ae%b5%e9%bd%8a%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd-%e7%be%a4%e6%a0%b8%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e6%9a%ab%e8%bc%83%e6%8b%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/00068.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 17:29:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "812萬購將軍澳維景灣畔2房戶  一手業主2004年買入 物業升值逾2倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">利嘉閣地產將軍澳都會駅分行促成將軍澳維景灣畔9座高層D室的二手成交個案，單位實用面積約498方呎，屬2房間隔，望市景。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">據悉，原業主2004年以約258.8萬元一手購入，持貨至今轉售，帳面獲利逾553萬元，期內物業升值約2.1倍。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該屋苑目前放盤量約25個，最低入場費由約700萬元起。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15880395-812%e8%90%ac%e8%b3%bc%e5%b0%87%e8%bb%8d%e6%be%b3%e7%b6%ad%e6%99%af%e7%81%a3%e7%95%942%e6%88%bf%e6%88%b6-%e4%b8%80%e6%89%8b%e6%a5%ad%e4%b8%bb2004%e5%b9%b4%e8%b2%b7%e5%85%a5-%e7%89%a9%e6%a5%ad%e5%8d%87",
